---

<MainLayout>
  <Header />
  <div class='wrapper'>
    <h2>~ The Comics! üôåüèª ~</h2>
    <a href='/comic-pages/comic-1'>Comic #1: Concussion</a>
    <a href='/comic-pages/comic-2'>Comic #2: Cookies</a>
